               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of the Assumption of Mary, መልክአ፡ ፍልሰታ፡ ለማርያም፡, Praise of the Beloved in Honor of Mary, ስብሐተ፡ ፍቁር፡; Various Hymns to Mary; Book of the night hours of Abba Giyorgis, መጽሐፈ፡ ሰዓታት፡ ዘአባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="3v" facs="003">Fols 1r–3v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2932RepCh213">Malkǝʾa
                                                  fǝlsatā</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለፍልሰተ፡ ሥጋኪ፡ ምስለ፡ ነፍስኪ፡ ኢመዋቲ፡</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="30r" to="36v" facs="032">Fols 30r–36v</locus><title>Praise of the Beloved in Honor of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ስብሐተ፡ ፍቁር፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ተዓብዮ፡ ነፍስየ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ በል፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ብፅዕት፡ አንቲ፡ ወንግሥተ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ዘሜንኒ፡ ማርያም፡ መንበረ፡ ሥላቅ፡ ታቦትነ፡ አንቲ፡ እንተ፤ ወርቅ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="10v" facs="013">Fols 10v and following</locus><title>Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, O My Lady Mary, the Angels Praise You in Heaven</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦ፡ እግኢእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ መላእክት፡ ይሴብሑኪ፡ በዓርያም፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="10v" to="12v" facs="013">Fols 10v–12v</locus><title>Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, Clothed in Golden Dress”</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦዑዕፍተ፡ ልብሰ፡ ወርቅ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="12v" to="13v" facs="015">Fols 12v–13v</locus><title>Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, O My Lady Mary, A Tree, Ever Verdant,” <foreign xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ዕፅ፡ ልምሉም፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="13v" to="14v" facs="016">Fols 13v–14v</locus><title>Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, O My Lady Mary, Life of the World.”</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦእግዚእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ሕይወተ፡ ዓለም፡</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
