                                                  ḫǝllinā</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ኦ፡ ርኅርኅተ፡ ሕሊና፡ ዘአፍቅሮተ፡ ሰብ፡ ልማዳ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="18r" to="19r" facs="020">Fols 18r–19r</locus><title>Hymn to Mary, “I Praise They Grace, O One Who is Full of Grace</title>
